at.ac.tuwien.ims.latex2mobiformulaconv.converter.mathml2html.elements

Class Formula

  • java.lang.Object
    • at.ac.tuwien.ims.latex2mobiformulaconv.converter.mathml2html.elements.Formula

  • public class Formula
extends Object
    Main model for a single formula found in a LaTeX input document

    Holds all relevant information for source and destination representation after successful conversion.

    Author:
    Michael Au√ü Created: 20.05.14 23:30

      • invalid

        private boolean invalid
        A FormulaConverter can set this flag to true for removing this formula from the output markup.

        Default value is false, even if the formula object is not been initialized properly yet. It is up to the Formula Converter to determine if the resulting output is invalid.
